    "These factors relate to the balance of exploration and exploitation, the enhanced exploration of the solution space, and the improved adaptability to complex environments.",
    "This dual-factor reward system prompted RL agents to not only find scenarios with long execution times but also to ensure these scenarios were varied and representative of different operational conditions.Columns RL * of Table 5.2 show the results of RL agents for both case studies.",
    "For the 6-DOF case study, agents utilizing a reward strategy based on diversity achieved better results.",
    "Also, the statistical analysis indicates the RL PPO ED values significantly surpass RL PPO E values (p-value=3.05 × 10 -6, α < 0.01), and RL A2C ED values exceed RL PPO E values (p-value=5.57 × 10 -6, α < 0.01).",
    "However, the comparison between RL A2C ED and RL PPO ED yields a non-significant difference (p-value=0.37, α < 0.01), suggesting no substantial difference between the two algorithms."
